        <h3>Can I use this website without a PayPal account?</h3>
        No, sadly not. The only way to pay on our website is to use PayPal. However, PayPal is a simple to use and widely accepted electronic banking medium; for more information see
        <a href="https://www.paypal.com/za/home"> here</a>
        <h3>How do I add a product to my cart?</h3>
        Once you have found a product you are interested in, you simply click the "Add To Cart" button located directly below the item's price. Once you have added the item to your
        cart you will see that it appears there with the quantity you are interested in buying and the total for your order.
        <h3>How do I remove an item from my order?</h3>
        You simply click the "Remove Item" checkbox on the item in your checkout you are not interested in and then click the "Update" button below the Shopping Cart list.
        <h3>Do I need an account to buy things?</h3>
        Yes you do need to have an account to buy things on our store; however, you can simply use your google sign in details.
        <h3>How do I buy a product I am interested in?</h3>
        <br />
         Once you are satisfied with your order you can click the checkout
        button and be transfered to your login page - from then on you simply enter in your sign in details (if you aren't already signed in) and then continue to the PayPal login. Once
        you have signed in to the PayPal page, you can buy your products and proceed through the checkout.
